有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n題外話 <br />\n雙普選都係基本法清楚寫明 每個人都有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n但都唔知去咗邊到"},{"pid":"36d0543cba4f74869d472c90079241af506abaca","tid":1736452,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72775766_146039523434534_8546505068113821696_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEuSyVTeYeEiayBTRrvkHRos4tQQbTg9Rj6oUJRvY1p8cG0jX-vDbd3LqBNfqZ2d-eusP6sq_D-YsfhIoXKYWWo2TFYW0AV-tUs1BfX7YsiCQ&amp;_nc_oc=AQkwMmRDhTawlWbH4aoOpYieSK2oDEUAYCRszXggLDiwV0k97K6DYdqXs3KHeq8J5QM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=24190d0bd4a6a5c85b4dd0c78123d9d4&amp;oe=5E4E59D9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72775766_146039523434534_8546505068113821696_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEuSyVTeYeEiayBTRrvkHRos4tQQbTg9Rj6oUJRvY1p8cG0jX-vDbd3LqBNfqZ2d-eusP6sq_D-YsfhIoXKYWWo2TFYW0AV-tUs1BfX7YsiCQ%26_nc_oc%3DAQkwMmRDhTawlWbH4aoOpYieSK2oDEUAYCRszXggLDiwV0k97K6DYdqXs3KHeq8J5QM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D24190d0bd4a6a5c85b4dd0c78123d9d4%26oe%3D5E4E59D9&h=3e2821ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65864d0cad864622e318e8d865e3abfdc0900a02","tid":1736452,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b94ac4c441cc6dd980ded82eb0c39f96fc6dbfd5","tid":1736452,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"唔係紅磡指揮官咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:00:56.000Z","msg":"係，我記錯，多謝指正! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb262e0dd19ba4b54c51f22263594858a16be65f","tid":1736452,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"744c91f75447a6f407c3f